headline: Parker Declares Quarterly Cash Dividend
summary: CLEVELAND, Oct. 22, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Parker Hannifin Corporation (NYSE: PH), the global leader in motion and control technologies, today announced that its Board of Directors has declared a regular quarterly cash dividend of $1.80 per share of common stock to shareholders of record as of November 7, 2025. headline: Parker Hannifin Is Up More Than 20% Since our Recommendation. The Stock Is Still Cheap.
summary: From the sleek designs of military jets to the pleasing swoop of an airplane’s wing, humans have always found flight fascinating.  The stock has risen more than 20% since Barron’s highlighted it in the summer of 2024.  Parker Hannifin  shares aren’t likely to take investors on a bumpy ride.
